express 安装

localhost:~/peng$ sudo npm install -g express-generator                                                                                                  
[sudo] leo 的密码： 
/opt/node/node-v8.9.4-linux-x64/bin/express -> /opt/node/node-v8.9.4-linux-x64/lib/node_modules/express-generator/bin/express-cli.js
+ express-generator@4.15.5
added 6 packages in 3.365s
localhost:~/peng$ sudo ln -s /opt/node/node-v8.9.4-linux-x64/bin/express /usr/local/bin/express
localhost:~/peng$ cd blog/
localhost:~/peng/blog$ npm install
localhost:~/peng/blog$ DEBUG=blog ./bin/www #启动
localhost:3000


npm install express -g # 安装express模块
npm install -g express-generator (4.0及以后版本都得使用)
npm -V # 查看express版本号 

express app
node app.js
Cannot find module 'express'
解决方案
npm install express或者配置环境
Cannot find module 'serve-favicon'
npm install serve-favicon
Cannot find module 'morgan'
npm install morgan
Cannot find module 'cookie-parser'
npm install cookie-parser
Cannot find module 'body-parser'
npm install body-parser

npm uninstall -g express
npm install -g express@3.0
express app
cd app
node app.js
Cannot find module 'express'
npm install express@3.0
node app.js
Express server listening on port 3000
http://127.0.0.1:3000/
Express
500 Error: Cannot find module 'jade'
npm install jade

修改route/js文件后 要重新node app.js页面内容才会修改